# ─── DayBridge — Environment Reference ──────────────────────────────────────
#
# THIS FILE IS A REFERENCE ONLY. The app does not read from .env at runtime.
#
# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │  CLIENT_ID and TENANT_ID are hardcoded in auth.js                      │
# │  All other secrets are set in Azure portal → Configuration             │
# │  This file is blocked by .gitignore — never committed to git           │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# WHERE EACH VALUE LIVES:
#
#   CLIENT_ID      → hardcoded in auth.js  (public SPA value, not a secret)
#   TENANT_ID      → hardcoded in auth.js  (public SPA value, not a secret)
#   JIRA_*         → Azure portal → DayBridge → Configuration (server-side only)
#   CLAUDE_API_KEY → Azure portal → DayBridge → Configuration (server-side only)

# ─── Azure AD App Registration (hardcoded in auth.js — public values) ────────
CLIENT_ID=50575903-5945-4162-b6ad-8d9ad175034d
TENANT_ID=a3be1280-7a3a-4edc-b258-0d6a539beee9

# ─── Jira Cloud (set in Azure portal Configuration — NOT in source code) ─────
JIRA_BASE_URL=https://wallstreetdocs.atlassian.net
JIRA_EMAIL=kobir.hosan@wsd.com
JIRA_TOKEN=your-jira-api-token-here
# Get token: https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens

# ─── Anthropic Claude (set in Azure portal Configuration — NOT in source code)
CLAUDE_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
# Get key: https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys
